@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<h4>Welcome to GarageKeeper, your trusted partner in vehicle management! 🛠️🚗</h4>

<p>
    At GarageKeeper, we understand that your garage is more than just a place to store cars—it's where your passion for vehicles thrives. We're committed to ensuring your data is as secure as your most prized automobile. Below, you'll find our privacy policy, crafted to give you peace of mind as you manage your garage operations with us.
</p>

<ol>
    <li>
        <strong>User Data - Secure and Confidential:</strong>
        <p>We collect basic information such as your name, email, and contact details to create and manage your account. Rest assured, your personal information is guarded as carefully as a collector's edition car in a locked garage.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Vehicle Information - Your Garage, Your Control:</strong>
        <p>Your vehicle data, including make, model, service history, and maintenance records, is kept confidential. Only you and our trusted system have access to these details, ensuring your garage operates smoothly and efficiently.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Appointment Scheduling - Streamlined and Private:</strong>
        <p>When you schedule appointments for maintenance or repairs, your schedule is treated with utmost confidentiality. We only share the necessary details with the technicians responsible for your service.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Service Orders - Precision and Privacy:</strong>
        <p>Details about the services performed on your vehicles are stored securely. Whether it's a routine checkup or a major overhaul, only authorized personnel can access your service orders.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Invoices - Clear and Confidential:</strong>
        <p>Your payment information and invoice details are handled with the highest level of security. We make sure that your billing experience is as smooth and straightforward as possible, without compromising your privacy.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Company Expenses - Transparent and Accountable:</strong>
        <p>If you're managing expenses within GarageKeeper, you can trust that your financial data is stored securely and only accessible to those with the appropriate permissions.</p>
    </li>
</ol>

<p>
    <strong>Security and Confidentiality:</strong>
    At GarageKeeper, your data's security is our top priority. We use advanced security measures to protect your information, and our team is committed to maintaining your trust by upholding strict confidentiality standards.
</p>

<p>
    Thank you for choosing GarageKeeper to manage your garage operations. Whether you're scheduling appointments, tracking vehicle maintenance, or handling invoices, we're here to support your passion for vehicles with a secure and user-friendly platform.
</p>

<p>
    Driven by a love for all things automotive,
    The GarageKeeper Team 🛠️🚗
</p>
